lth and safety compliance for Texas-based company ITN.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 735, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oklahoma_Sooners_football\", \"score\": 0.8693604281954803, \"rank\": 0.1446276025094575, \"text\": \"Oklahoma\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oklahoma_Sooners_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oklahoma_Sooners_football\"}, {\"begin\": 842, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITN\", \"score\": 0.9994594652785893, \"rank\": 0.0005408270569976392, \"text\": \"ITN\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITN\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toAmericato study\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"Fincham-Dukes\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 775}, {\"ngram\": \"health and safety compliance\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because of that, the 27-year-old is forced to wake up at 5am to train before sneaking in another season in the evening after his day at the office.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another season\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"the evening\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"his day\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"the office\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite his impressive showing against the odds in Paris, Fincham-Dukes revealed he will have little time to savour his finish as he must return to America in time for work on Friday - just 72 hours after his final jump.\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999914357431, \"rank\": 8.564181381338496e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his impressive showing\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"the odds\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"Fincham-Dukes\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"little time\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"his finish\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1152}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1160}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"his final jump\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I really hope I have done myself justice because I work full-time, I am back at work on Friday,' he told the BBC after the final.\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1329, \"end\": 1332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9806031646610905, \"rank\": 0.017450461829193745, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"justice\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So I am carrying a lot of extra stress that these guys do not have to deal with.\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"extra stress\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"these guys\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have carried myself tremendously well this year.\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1485, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fourth at Europeans, fifth at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [], \"nou